Author: RockyLeesya
Title: [BOUNTY] KICKCITY! BOUNTY IS OVER, THANK YOU.
Body: KickCity protocol is designed to be fair. This means that P2P marketing structure is not a pyramid. It's marketing on the same level. Every promoter gets equal distribution of tokens if they contributed equal result based promotional power. Time or order of invitation does not play any role in the system. A user who has more conversion via his link or invitations earns more.

Author: HansakaMadushan
Title: [BOUNTY] KICKCITY! BOUNTY IS OVER, THANK YOU.
Body: The event industry is undergoing metamorphosis and KickCity is one of the companies leading this. A few years ago, tickets were bought or sold offline. Now it's happening online. The new phase of event ticketing is based on social interaction. Users don't just want to buy tickets, but know and interact with fellow attendees before, during and after events. Moreover, with the growing speed of the internet, anyone would be able to set up a processing gateway and accept tickets for his events. Therefore, Event platforms of the future will be fully built around people. Event communities  decentralized or centralized.

Author: needmoney
Title: [BOUNTY] KICKCITY! BOUNTY IS OVER, THANK YOU.
Body: Hello everyone, we are locking the thread to prevent cheaters from adding reports to their previous messages.  You can contact us directly from Telegram regarding any problem and we will solve it.  @TokenSuiteSerkan   1. I put wrong information. How can I change it? - You should go ahead and let us know what needs to be changed on the bounty thread. 2. Why I was excluded from bounty campaign? - You didn't met the requirements. Make sure you entered true information. 3. Am I too late to join bounty campaign? - The bounty will last for 2 more weeks. 4. Is KYC necessary to receive tokens earned from bounty? - It is not necessary to have KYC for bounty tokens. 5. Why haven't you counted some of my weeks? - Except for signature program, all stakes will be fully counted at the end of the program. This includes Twitter program as well so please do not ask about it.  PLEASE ONLY USE BOUNTY THREAD FOR SUPPORT.      Decentralized Event Management & Marketing Protocol on Blockchain   Token Sale starts on 1st March 2018!   Website | Whitepaper | Twitter | Facebook | Telegram | ANN Thread | Github | Reddit | Medium   This bounty campaign will last for ONLY 4 WEEKS. Kickcity team is offering 2 200 000 tokens which are equal to $225,000 through this program.    Bounty Allocation  Signature Bounty 30% -  660 000 Tokens Youtube/Blogging Bounty 20% - 440 000 Tokens Twitter Bounty 20% -  440 000 Tokens Translation Bounty 20% - 440 000 Tokens Telegram Bounty 10% - 220 000 Tokens   General Rules  Signature stakes will be distributed every week, other stakes will be calculated end of the campaign. First week of the bounty campaign will start on 15th of February, Thursday. For any questions regarding the bounty campaign please use this thread. We reserve our right to eliminate you if we think you haven't been honest with your work. We reserve the right to change bounty campaign rules.   Signature Campaign   Weekly Rewards: Jr. Member: 0.5 stake per week Member: 0.75 stake per week Full Member: 1 stake per week (+0.25 stake for avatar) Senior Member: 1,5 stakes per week (+0,25 stake for avatar) Hero Member: 2 stakes per week (+0,25 stake for avatar) Legendary: 2,25 stakes per week (+0,25 stake for avatar)   Signature Campaign Rules: Participants have to be at least Jr. Member. Every participants must wear our signature and personal text. Multiple accounts will be banned if spotted. Spam is not allowed. We expect you to post 10 constructive posts per week. Only 3 of these posts can be in local boards. Posts should be made in altcoin sections, local board included (excluding bounties sections). You will have to keep wearing our signature, avatar and personal text until the end of the first round. Do not fill the form without wearing our signature, or you will be rejected.   Apply: https://goo.gl/forms/mE7bXZHBVnGHh3at2 Spreadsheet: https://goo.gl/Nk9u24    Youtube/Blogging/Article Campaign  You will have to apply to us with your Youtube channel before start working. Youtube videos must be at least 1 minutes long. You must have at least 200 organic subscribers. You should have links to our website and whitepaper. Your Medium/Steem.it or any other free blogging blog page should have at least 250 followers. Your article must be original and contain at least 300 words. You should have links to our website and whitepaper. You will get stakes based on the quality and popularity of your work, reviewed at the end of the campaign.   Apply: https://goo.gl/forms/Yffxe6KWQhMLu0Xt2 Spreadsheet of accepted works: https://goo.gl/Nk9u24     Twitter Campaign  All participants must follow our official Twitter account. Your audit score must be more than 90%. We will check every participant to make sure their Twitter account is genuine. Your Twitter account must be mainly about cryptocurrencies. We will also accept media personalities. You have to have at least 1000 real followers. Everyone has to report their Likes and Retweets every week. You can report max 3 Retweets and Likes. To help with this, we will add dates on the Twitter spreadsheet on weeks.   Stakes: (stakes double if you have more than 10 000 followers) We will accept anyone with more than %90 audit score. If you have more than 1000 followers you'll get: - 0.5 stake for retweeting - 0.5 stake for like If you have less than 1000 followers you'll get: - 0.25 stake for retweeting - 0.25 stake for like   Apply: https://goo.gl/forms/1bX3cGPfqQvyfnOw1 Spreadsheet: https://goo.gl/Nk9u24    Translation Campaign  We will only ask you to translate ANN thread and whitepaper. If we find out you've used Google Translate, you will be banned from the campaign as a whole. You are expected to moderate and update your thread with our news and updates to our ANN thread, at least once a week. You are expected to finish article translation in 2 days after you've assigned with the job. We only limited number of languages, they will be selected from the most active communities on Bitcointalk. We are looking for Members or above.   Apply: https://goo.gl/forms/TVdf08iaFsi4TJa03 Spreadsheet: https://goo.gl/Nk9u24   Telegram Campaign   Join our Telegram channel and get 1 stake! Total bounty allocated will be divided to the number of participants. We will give extra stake for active user on Telegram group. The activity we expect is to be an active member of the community engaging in discussions regularly. We do not ask you to say Hi to people.  JOIN THROUGH: https://t.me/kickcity_chat/  Apply: https://goo.gl/forms/r1KH3RzczhrDI3Ql1 Spreadsheet: https://goo.gl/Nk9u24
